                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8588" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1328</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2323 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“链”上发力，加“数”前行：铁骑力士全价值链降本增效的密码</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empowering the Value Chain, and Advancing with Digitization: The Code for Cost Reduction and Efficiency Increase Along the Full Value Chain of TECHLEX Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈扬，冯源（通讯作者），曾晓兰，王丽花，付嵘，林海芬</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">铁骑力士食品有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全价值链；降本增效；价值创造；铁骑力士；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Full value chain; Cost reduction and efficiency increase; Value creation; TECHLEX Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以农业产业化国家重点龙头企业——铁骑力士集团（简称“铁骑力士”）为研究对象，从该企业的创立到全产业链布局，以其价值链管理的前因后果为线索，按照事件发展顺序，详细阐述了该企业从行业竞争激烈、利润空间极度压缩、全产业链布局优势尚未显现的情况下，如何使用价值链管理实现企业价值链拉通以及降本增效的过程。本案例重点关注了企业围绕“打造全产业链，做中国高端食品领导者”这一目标进行的智慧养殖建设、产销协同、内外部价值链拉通、全面预算管理等变革措施，分析其如何在2022年和2023年分别达到了降本5.8亿元和3.94亿元的显著成效。通过本案例的学习和讨论，学员可以更好地理解在全产业链布局中，企业应该如何使用价值链管理实现降本增效，发挥全产业链优势，铸造核心竞争力，提升品牌价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study takes TECHLEX Group (hereinafter referred to as “TECHLEX”), a leading national enterprise in agriculture industrialization, as the research object. Starting from the establishment and complete industry chain layout of the enterprise, it follows the causes and consequences of the value chain management as the clue, and chronologically elaborates the process of how the enterprise streamline its value chain and enhance cost-effectiveness by value chain management under the multiple pressures of fierce external industry competition, extreme profit margin compression, and unmanifested advantages of complete industry chain layout. This case study focuses on the enterprise’s transformative measures such as intelligent farming construction, production-sales coordination, internal and external value chain integration, and comprehensive budget management in pursuit of the goal of “building a complete industry chain and becoming a leader in upmarket Chinese food.” The analysis reveals how TECHLEX achieved significant cost reductions of 580 million and 394 million yuan in 2022 and 2023 respectively. Through the study and discussion of this case, students can better understand how companies should utilize value chain management to enhance cost-effectiveness, leverage complete industry chain advantages, forge core competitiveness, and enhance brand value within the context of complete industry chain layout.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链理论；资源编排理论；业财融合理论；戴明循环</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
